<!--
    Hebrew (עברית) string resources.
    Android uses the legacy locale tag "iw" for Hebrew; this directory is therefore named
    values-iw/ even though the ISO 639-1 code is "he".

    RTL layout is handled automatically by the framework when the system locale (or the
    user-selected locale) is Hebrew. No explicit LayoutDirection overrides are needed in
    Compose because Material3 already respects CompositionLocalProvider(LocalLayoutDirection).
-->
